DESCRIPTION:Join us for a vibrant\, feel-good Queer Munch at a/stir—a space
	 to gather\, celebrate\, and connect over great food and even better compa
	ny. Whether you’re coming with friends\, a partner\, or flying solo\, this
	 is your invitation to show up exactly as you are and be part of a welcomi
	ng\, affirming community. Expect a delicious gluten-free menu\, tasty drin
	ks\, and a warm\, inclusive atmosphere filled with laughter\, conversation
	\, and queer joy. We’ll have music\, mingling\, and plenty of opportunitie
	s to meet new people and build connections.\n\n✨ All identities and expres
	sions are celebrated\n\n🥂 Food \\+ drinks available for purchase\n\n🌈 Come
